commit.message: Replaced experimental import to stable import for ADF. Fixed pose translation
Used constants and added minor documentation
Aligned to Area Description frame instead of Start of Service
Downloading now reads as a binary file
Added handlers for synchronous thread requests to reduce crashes
ADFs can be uploaded and downloaded. There are concurrency and timing issues still.
Augmented reality object now appears with device. Coordinate frames unaligned.
Allocating session on the heap instead of using file I/o
Always sends position to server even if not localized
Added session data files to gitignore
Modified app to reflect changes of session modularization on the server
Modularized sessions into separate files and directories
